    s.say(" For heritage tour, architecture, Hindu pilgrimage, wildlife tour, birdwatching, cultural tour, handicraft and art, food tour, shopping, chikankari and brass work, Buddhist pilgrimage, Jain pilgrimage, Christian pilgrimage, and for sighting the iconic Taj Mahal.")
